409
00:20:56,167 --> 00:20:59,378
NEVERTHELESS, I HAVE DECIDED
TO PLACE MY FAITH IN YOU

410
00:20:59,378 --> 00:21:02,673
AND I AM ENTRUSTING YOU WITH
MY LAST AND GREATEST HOPE:

411
00:21:02,673 --> 00:21:04,467
THE FULL ABILITIES OF
THE GN DRIVE.

412
00:21:05,801 --> 00:21:08,095
I PRAY THAT YOU WILL
CONTINUE FIGHTING

413
00:21:08,095 --> 00:21:10,514
IN ORDER TO ATTAIN
TRUE PEACE

414
00:21:10,514 --> 00:21:14,060
AND ERADICATE THE SCOURGE
OF WAR FROM OUR PLANET.

415
00:21:14,060 --> 00:21:16,646
NOT FOR THE SAKE OF
CELESTIAL BEING,

416
00:21:16,646 --> 00:21:19,982
BUT OF YOUR OWN WILL,
TOGETHER WITH YOUR GUNDAMS.

417
00:21:22,485 --> 00:21:24,487
GUNDAM...

418
00:21:26,530 --> 00:21:28,783
I DON'T KNOW WHAT MAGIC TRICK
YOU'RE PULLING HERE!

419
00:21:32,995 --> 00:21:34,789
I SHOULDN'T BE LOSING!

420
00:21:34,789 --> 00:21:36,707
(Attacking yell)

421
00:21:36,707 --> 00:21:38,501
(Slash)

422
00:21:38,501 --> 00:21:40,169
(Boom)

423
00:21:42,046 --> 00:21:44,882
WHAT THE...
WHAT THE HELL WAS THAT?

424
00:21:53,599 --> 00:21:57,144
THE TRANS‐AM SYSTEM.

425
00:21:57,144 --> 00:21:59,272
SO THIS IS...

426
00:21:59,272 --> 00:22:02,024
THE TRANS‐AM!

