433
00:23:43,292 --> 00:23:46,337
Narrator:
HE WANTED TO CHANGE THE WORLD
AND THE WILL OF THE PEOPLE.

434
00:23:46,337 --> 00:23:49,840
BUT NOW HE RAGES AGAINST
THOSE THOUGHTS.

435
00:23:49,840 --> 00:23:52,635
